Epic, I know you will not see my comment, but I created a very interesting concept. It is so, if a person, for example, had bought a battle pass, and cannot play, at that time, he could have in the challenge tab, the option to replace the battle pass for him. EXAMPLE:
a guy bought the season 6 battle pass, but because he was traveling he didn't complete the pass. He is very sad, but when this concept arrives in the game, the pass from chapter 2 would be replaced by the one from 6 for FREE, and so when he finishes pass 6, the pass of the moment comes back to him
